The '''Eredain''', or the '''Schweizerische Tolkien Gesellschaft''', was the Swiss [[Tolkien Societies|Tolkien Society]]. It was founded on [[25 March|March 25]], [[1986]] and disbanded in the summer of [[2006]]. In [[1996]], they founded [[Walking Tree Publishers]], which does still exist.
